# RSI washout with volume confirmation. Risk-based sizing: the position
# is sized so a stop-out costs exactly 1% of equity, which is why the
# [stop 2%] tag is required (the compiler enforces the pairing).

strategy "Oversold Bounce"

universe [mega_tech]
timeframe 1d

when [rsi] < 30 and [volume_spike 1.5x]
  buy [risk 1%]

sell when [rsi] crosses above 55
  or [stop 2%]
